snippet.title: What’s really going on between Johnny Depp & Amber Heard?! | Tarot Reading
snippet.description:
THESE CELEBRITY READINGS ARE FOR ENTERTAINMENT PURPOSES. 

BOOK A READING TODAY! Check out: 
https://fullmoontarot.youcanbook.me

All inquiries including reading requests, please email:
FullMoonPriestessTarot@gmail.com

Donate to my channel! 
1. Tip jar: https://www.paypal.me/love2221111
2. You can donate an Oracle or Tarot deck in exchange for a private reading of your choice. 

FOLLOW ME ON IG:
SPIRITUAL: https://www.instagram.com/FullMoonPriestess
PERSONAL: https://www.Instagram.com/EarthAngelJessica

I’m an intuitive reader. I use tarot and Oracle cards to determine, visually, what my guides are telling me about the particular situation. I have been reading tarot for about 5 years now and don’t plan on stopping but improving every year. I love reading about love and relationships and find celebrity couple readings to be indirectly related to all of us . I do not permit gossip or any negativity on my channel. I like an audience who is “being nice”, particularly understanding and practicing compassion because that is the type of reader I am. Any other vibes I receive that are not beneficial to anyone, I do not acknowledge or entertain it.
